{"tid":1742670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱青城一邊屌泛民人血選票但又派成5隻熱狗選區議會係咩玩法?","createTime":"2019-11-21T01:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T05:11:38.000Z","uid":66260,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3449845ac0a79d0e28059cf3ae82cf73354cc14","tid":1742670,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"泛民主派 &middot; 永遠站在抗爭者對面<br />\n1 小時 &middot; <br />\n販民叫你去守poly ，話唔守住poly 就會退無死所。出左事搞到長春圍城就叫裡面嘅人自首，再叫其他人圍返poly 轉頭，結果拉左1400個。裡面嘅人要逃走，蘋果立場就不斷開live 影住你點走，篤完你魁之後香港人仲要話多謝蘋果日報。<br />\n<br />\n到最後叫你1124一定要出嚟投票，血就你地流，票就佢地攞。攞到議席就即時開記者會譴責前線好暴力，唔係同路人，be condom<br />\n<br />\n#大量訊息素<br />\n#販民害死人<br />\n#保長選舉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvuTzLO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvuTzLO.jpg&h=d1b4ce04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 自己個區得熱狗同保皇揀, 會含淚投熱狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125e8e7e11dc896878ee86a477e01047ae659d3c","tid":1742670,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:30:09.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e7c7ea99ca5820f34e2e6804a44ddcc91dca7f1","tid":1742670,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"唔理熱狗之前做過乜<br />\n但熱狗叫人唔好係中大同poly打陣地<br />\n不過無人理"},{"pid":"4f42f847df5598485f2e99910ea2947ebdf7d044","tid":1742670,"uid":66260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5e7c7ea99ca5820f34e2e6804a44ddcc91dca7f1","tid":1742670,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"唔理熱狗之前做過乜<br />\n但熱狗叫人唔好係中大同poly打陣地<br />\n不過無人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"連登一日幾百幾千個策略post, 貼